#-- | Description      :  This Program is used to loop through all the files in a        |
#-- |                     specified location and change their file permissions           |
#-- |                                                                                    |
#-- |Change Record:                                                                      |
#-- |===============                                                                     |
#-- |Version   Date         Author           Remarks                                     |
#-- |=======   ==========   =============    ======================                      |
